l regno delle due Sicilie |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fUIsAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA168|year=1848|publisher=dalle stampe di Ranucci|location=Naples|language=Italian|pages=511\u2013515}}\n*{{cite book|last=Cappelletti|first=Giuseppe|title=Le chiese d'Italia: dalla loro origine sino ai nostri giorni |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UwQVAAAAYAAJ|volume=vigesimo primo (21)|year=1870|publisher=G. Antonelli|location=Venezia|language=Italian|pages=165\u2013171}}\n*{{cite book|last=D'Agostino|first=Enzo|title=Da Locri a Gerace: storia di una diocesi della Calabria bizantina dalle origini al 1480|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BboD1dw8yU4C&pg=PA76|year=2004|publisher=Rubbettino Editore|location=Soveria Mannelli (Catanzaro)|language=Italian|isbn=978-88-498-1158-2}}\n*Gemelli, S. (ed.) (1986). ''La Cattedrale di Gerace. Il monumento, la funzione, I corredi''. Carical, Cosenza.\n*Kamp, Norbert (1975). ''Kirche und Monarchie im staufischen K\u00f6nigreich Sizilien: [http://digi20.digitale-sammlungen.de/de/fs1/object/display/bsb00042154_00001.html?prox=true&phone=true&ngram=true&seriesTitle_str=%7BKirche+und+Monarchie+im+staufischen+K%C3%B6nigreich+Sizilien%7D&hl=scan&fulltext=Kamp+Kirche+und+Monarchie&mode=simple&context=Kamp%20Kirche%20und%20Monarchie I. Prosopographische Grundlegung, Bistumer und  Bist\u00fcmer und Bisch\u00f6fe des Konigreichs 1194\u20131266: 2. Apulien und Calabrien]'' M\u00fcnchen: Wilhelm Fink 1975.\n*Kehr, Paulus Fridolin (1975). ''Italia pontificia. Regesta pontificum Romanorum.'' [http://sul-derivatives.stanford.edu/derivative?CSNID=00002441&mediaType=application/pdf Vol. X: Calabria\u2013Insulae].  Berlin: Weidmann. (in Latin)\n*{{cite book|author=Lanzoni, Francesco|title=Le diocesi d'Italia dalle origini al principio del secolo VII (an. 604)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fzlSAQAAMAAJ|year=1927|publisher=Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana|location=Rome|language=Italian|pages=}}\n*{{cite book|last1= Lobstein|first1=Franz von|last2=Sorge|first2=Giuseppe |title=Bollari dei vescovi di Gerace|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5HipHAAACAAJ|year=1977|publisher=Edizioni effe emme|location=Chiaravalle Centrale |language=Italian}}\n* Russo, Francesco (1982). ''Storia della Chiesa in Calabria dalle origini al Concilio di Trento,'' 2 vols. Rubbetino: Soveria Mannelli 1982.\n*{{cite book|last=Scaglione|first=Pasquale|title=Storie di Locri e Gerace|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZriLhMi_ZnEC&pg=PA13|volume=Parte seconda|year=1856|publisher=G. Nobile|location=Naples|page=}}\n*{{cite book|last=Taccone-Gallucci|first=Domenico|title=Regesti dei Romani pontefici della Calabria|url=https://archive.org/details/regestideiroman00galgoog|page=[https://archive.org/details/regestideiroman00galgoog/page/n349 402]|year=1902|publisher=Tip. Vaticana|location=Rome|language=Italian|pages=}}\n*{{cite book|last1=Ughelli|first1=Ferdinando|last2=Coleti|first2=Niccolo|title=Italia Sacra Sive De Episcopis Italiae, Et Insularum adiacentium|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SZtQAAAAcAAJ|volume=Tomus nonus (9)|year=1721|publisher=Antonio Coleti|location=Venice|language=Latin|pages=393\u2013399}}\n*{{cite book|title=Synodus dioecesana ab illustriss. et reverendiss d.d. Vincentio Vincentino ... celebrata in cathedrali ecclesia 9. kal. maij 1651|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-K1THeBlXNEC&pg=PA170|year=1651|publisher=typis haeredum Petri Breae|location=Messana|pages=169\u2013173}} (contains a list of bishops)\n\n====Acknowledgment====\n* {{Catholic|title=Gerace}}\n\n{{Roman Catholic Ecclesiastical Province of Reggio Calabria-Bova}}\n\n{{coord|38.2333|N|16.2667|E|source:wikidata|display=title}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Locri}}\n[[Category:Roman Catholic dioceses in Calabria]]\n[[Category:Dioceses established in the 5th century]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox diocese\n| jurisdiction      = Diocese<!-- Type of jurisdiction: i.e. Diocese or Archdiocese -->\n| name              = Locri-Gerace\n| latin         